author: The Critical Drinker
description: For a while there, she really did have it all. The looks, the style, the support of the Hollywood establishment. But beneath the winning smile and glamorous dresses, there lurked a web of lies, deception, abuse and... poop on beds. So how did Amber Heard become Amber Turd? Join me as we find out.
title: Crash And Burn - The Amber Heard Story
